Class GameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jme3.scene.control.AbstractControl
      • model.GameObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.jme3.export.Savable, com.jme3.scene.control.Control, com.jme3.util.clone.JmeCloneable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Obstacle, Player, Terrain

    public abstract class GameObject
extends com.jme3.scene.control.AbstractControl
    This object represents the basic object used in this game. All objects in this game will be extending this class.
    Since:
    Saturday, 4 November 2017
